import './search-bar.css' export default function SearchBar(props) { let div = document.createElement("div"), input = document.createElement("input"), button = document.createElement("button") document.body.appendChild(div) div.appendChild(input) div.appendChild(button) div.id = "search-bar" input.id = "search-bar-input" button.id = "search-bar-button" input.type = "text" input.placeholder = config.placeholder button.onclick = config.onsubmit return (
) }
